title: The tragedy of Trump's refusal to concede
description: Trump could have started with a gracious concession speech, congratulating President-elect Joe Biden on his impressive victory, writes Julian Zelizer. Instead, he is living in his own alternate reality, and forcing government officials to play along.

author: Paul Gittings, CNN
title: No.1 Dustin Johnson on record run as he leads Masters by four-shots
description: Dustin Johnson lived up to his billing as the world's top golfer to open up a four-shot third-round lead as a "tired" Tiger Woods saw his hopes of defending his Masters crown disappear Saturday at Augusta National.

title: Federal judge says new DACA rules are invalid
description: Chad Wolf was not legally serving as acting Homeland Security secretary when he signed rules limiting DACA applications and renewals, and those rules are now invalid, a federal judge ruled Saturday.
